## Pre-Deploy Checklist (run before every `vercel --prod` or `git push`)

- [ ] `npm run build` exits 0 in `banking_api_ui/`
- [ ] No new `console.error` or unhandled rejections in browser console
- [ ] Admin login â†’ callback â†’ `/admin` dashboard works
- [ ] User login â†’ callback â†’ `/dashboard` works
- [ ] BankingAgent FAB visible on login page (unauthenticated)
- [ ] BankingAgent shows banking actions after login
- [ ] Direct navigation to `/config`, `/dashboard` returns the page (not 404)
- [ ] OAuth callbacks redirect to correct hostname (not localhost)
- [ ] MCP tool calls succeed (Accounts, Transactions, Balance)

