## Change Budget Rules (Layer 3)

- Name the component (`UserDashboard`, `Header`, `BankingAgent`, etc.)
- Name the specific element (button, color, padding, class)
- Say "do not touch" for adjacent code you want preserved
- One logical change per request â€” multiple changes = regression risk
- Never clean up unrelated code during a feature/fix

